    m_Localized: Pull tab from an aluminum beverage can.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900237
    m_Localized: Pull tab
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947089
    m_Localized: An unidentified aluminum pull tab from a beer bottle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900238
    m_Localized: Crushed aluminum foil
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947090
    m_Localized: "A heavily deformed and damaged aluminum p\xE2t\xE9 container."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900239
    m_Localized: Lead Bullet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947091
    m_Localized: Bullet from a percussion firearm, probably from the Thirty Years'
      War period.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900240
    m_Localized: Large Lead Bullet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947092
    m_Localized: Lead bullet from a carbine originating from the 19th century.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900241
    m_Localized: Spindle whorl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947093
    m_Localized: A spindle whorl made of lead or its alloy, most likely dated to
      the Middle Ages. It has a circular shape and a rectangular cross-section. The
      central hole was cast slightly off-center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900242
    m_Localized: Lead Crucifix
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947094
    m_Localized: Medieval lead cross probably worn around the neck.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1446878900243
    m_Localized: Iron fibula
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3871970947095
